title: Okuma Sierra Fly Reel Specifications
textBeforeTable: Easy To Change Left To Right Hand Retrieval Conversion.  ALC: Alumilite Diecast Aluminum Frame Precision Machined Stainless Steel Spool Shaft Precision Machined Brass Bushing Drive System Roller bearing allows the drag to engage in one direction only Fully Adjustable Teflon And Stainless Drag System Features: Whether you are a first time fly angler or a guide looking for something new, the Okuma Sierra series offers quality designed to last a lifetime. The fly reel that started it all for Okuma more than a decade ago has only grown better with age. Representing the ultimate value in a simple and reliable fly reel, Sierra's Alumalite frame, one-way roller bearing and Teflon/stainless steel drag system puts a smile on your face every trip out. The Okuma Sierra's affordability allows for a complete selection of line types to be carried and deployed at a moment's notice.
